<genericPage guid="ee2a0a82-ac4d-4783-b3f7-df808fd9c834" id="58414" nodeName="Service" isDoc="" updated="2024-11-21T16:58:28.8530000Z" parentGUID="1e437ab1-de9c-402a-bf63-da580ffe1715" nodeTypeAlias="genericPage" templateAlias="GenericResponsive" sortOrder="11" published="true" isBlueprint="false">
  <bannerDropdown><![CDATA[Ski Holidays]]></bannerDropdown>
  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<p><img src="/media/13107237/inghams-service-offering-900x600.jpg" alt="InghamsServiceOffering" data-udi="umb://media/b186abe62a654889884959f0a6c862bb" /></p>
<h2>Why travel with Inghams</h2>
<p>Whether it’s <a data-udi="umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416" href="/{localLink:umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416}" title="Walking Holidays">walking</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/25e767db044444389ae09383681f982e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/25e767db044444389ae09383681f982e}" title="Ski Holidays">skiing</a> or <a data-udi="umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0}" title="Lapland Holidays">Lapland adventures</a>, all of our holidays are based on your passions and interests and making the most of what the great outdoors has to offer.</p>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Your holiday with Inghams</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img style="width: 95px; height: 28px;" src="/media/13107196/whats-included-with-inghams.jpg?width=95&amp;height=28" alt="WhatsIncludedWithInghams" data-udi="umb://media/1075e5d667ab411580a93714ac65208f" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Travel, accommodation, transport &amp; Destination Expert all included</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us to book today</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<h3><span>Inghams service highlights</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><span>No matter the type of holiday you chose with us, a <strong>Resort representative</strong> is available throughout your holiday either in person or over the phone to help answer any questions, share valuable knowledge or guide you through your stay.</span></li>
<li>Inghams has <strong>90 years' worth</strong> of knowledge, with expert staff to ensure your holiday is a once in a lifetime experience. <span></span></li>
<li>Our <strong>Chalet service</strong> is of the highest quality - with our Chalet Hosts there to offer dining, drinks and resort knowledge during your <a data-udi="umb://document/25e767db044444389ae09383681f982e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/25e767db044444389ae09383681f982e}" title="Ski Holidays">Ski Holiday</a>.</li>
<li><strong>Guided walks</strong> are on offer throughout the vast majority of our <a data-udi="umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416" href="/{localLink:umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416}" title="Walking Holidays">Walking Holidays</a>, step out across some of Europe's most scenic routes.</li>
<li>Do not miss our once in a lifetime, all-encompassing holidays to Lapland, with over <strong>25 years' experience</strong> in providing <a data-udi="umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0}" title="Lapland Holidays">Lapland Holidays</a>, Inghams will ensure you the most magical of adventures. </li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img style="width: 300px; height: 76px;" src="/media/13107830/inghams-90-years-300.jpg?width=300&amp;height=76" alt="Inghams90Years" data-udi="umb://media/1d391c2e5ed34ec68c303db69f93a2e2" /></p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2>Before, during &amp; after your holiday</h2>
<p>We are here to support you. Booking an Inghams holiday means...</p>
<div> </div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><img style="width: 201px; height: 200px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13107192/ing-phone.png?width=201&amp;height=200" alt="BeforeYourInghamsHoliday" data-udi="umb://media/26e85b2c2878414997d1f490bb9b6354" /></p>
<h3>Before your holiday</h3>
<ul>
<li>You have the support of our reservations team via phone, email and web chat during your booking journey.</li>
<li>Pre-departure emails with information, holiday inspiration and support regarding your upcoming holiday.</li>
<li>The <a rel="noopener" href="https://my.inghams.co.uk/login" target="_blank" title="My Booking">My Booking</a> section on the website to check the details of your booking at any time. </li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div></div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><img style="width: 200px; height: 209px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13107193/ing-rep.png?width=200&amp;height=209" alt="DuringYourInghamsHoliday" data-udi="umb://media/9221570647f541b980a9ab0eabf1ba29" /></p>
<h3>During your holiday</h3>
<ul>
<li>Reassurance of a resort representative, either in resort or over the phone.</li>
<li>Assistance or advice regarding your accommodation, transfers or in resort information</li>
<li>Should an emergency arise in resort, we will do our very best to arrange for a member of the team to be with you in person.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div></div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><img style="width: 195px; height: 190px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13107194/ing-thums-up.png?width=195&amp;height=190" alt="AfterYourInghamsHoliday" data-udi="umb://media/007f11696f144206a845012b495e4ca0" /></p>
<h3>After your holiday</h3>
<ul>
<li>Our guest relations team are available via phone, email and web chat to hear your feedback and assist with any queries you may have.</li>
<li>Please do not hesitate to contact us should you have any post-holiday questions.</li>
<li>If you are looking to then book your next holiday, we will certainly be happy to assist.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13107199/inghams-service-resort-rep-800x200.jpg" alt="InghamsResortRep" data-udi="umb://media/b3392e723d5645c1957a864c565dc6c2" /></h2>
<h2>Why book with Inghams</h2>
<p>90 years of travel knowledge, shared with you. We know how, then and now...</p>
<p><img style="width: 500px; height: 250px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13107899/inghams-core-usps.png?width=500&amp;height=250" alt="InghamsCoreUSPs" data-udi="umb://media/9bc7ae11cab44b83a8a30f690f73611b" /></p>
<h4>FAQ's</h4>
<p>If you have questions about holidaying with us, you may find the answers in our <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/guest-services/frequently-asked-questions" target="_blank">FAQ section</a>.</p>
<h4>Send us a message</h4>
<p>Why not get in touch via our <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/stay-in-touch/contact-us" target="_blank">online contact form</a>. You can send us a question about any aspect of your holiday and we will get back to you as soon as we can.</p>
<h4>Travel updates</h4>
<p><span>For the latest travel advice and Snow Guarantee information - <a data-udi="umb://document/07103f762dbc49e9897a444ad4103338" href="/{localLink:umb://document/07103f762dbc49e9897a444ad4103338}" title="Travel Advice">visit here</a></span></p>
<p><span>For the latest snow reports, updated weekly throughout the season - <a data-udi="umb://document/3464b8f6fd3f41d9b286f0b64dac2b79" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3464b8f6fd3f41d9b286f0b64dac2b79}" title="Snow">visit here</a></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><iframe width="830" height="400" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/TXU1afJpIdg?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen="" title="Inghams' Ski Representative Service | Inside Inghams | Inghams Ski"></iframe></span></p>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">How to book your holiday</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Travel, accommodation and transfers? We’ve got you covered. Book your holiday online or give us a call. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us to book today</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
